
                              MindVox [~^JOIN~^] Syntax


      Add       - Append a Vox Forums or Newsgroup to your JOINed Listing
      Configure - Configure  your  JOINed list  with Interactive  Prompts
      Delete    - Remove a Vox Forum or  Newsgroup from your  JOINed List
      Index     - Display  a  Complete  Listing  of  ALL  MindVox  Forums
      List      - Display a List of the Forums & Groups that you Read NOW
      Quit      - Exit  the JOIN  section  and return  to the  main  menu


      To obtain a complete listing of available sections, you may use the
 FORUMS (MindVox) and USENET (News) commands respectively, from the main menu.
